        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[简单看了一下  粤核酸的影分身之术  五个小程序都是同一个公司开发的   版本号也是同样的  包括更新时间
提供服务的域名不是同一个  主要域名有两个  
1:zdkqyy....]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<br>简单看了一下  粤核酸的影分身之术  五个小程序都是同一个公司开发的   版本号也是同样的  包括更新时间<br>提供服务的域名不是同一个  主要域名有两个  <br>1:zdkqyy.com(中山大学附属口腔医院)  2:gdwst.gov.cn(广东卫生和计划委员会) <br>五个域名解析的IP是连号的<br><br>以上是客观事实  下面来说一下我的猜测<br>1:同一套程序(由相同公司开发版本号相同更新时间相同  可信度80%以上)<br>2:服务器在同一个机房(由IP连号推测  可信度80%以上) <br>3:机房应该是当地政府和联通建立的(可信度80%)<br>4:关于他们为什么需要5个小程序  我的猜测是他们压根没用负载均衡  也就是说只有5台服务器(可信度60%不排除就是单纯想玩)<br>5:关于技术负责公司为什么不是腾讯  懂得都懂  不懂的就去查查这家公司业务<br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FqBh2PNiQ-npPhfpbHkCiIupRudTv2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FqBh2PNiQ-npPhfpbHkCiIupRudTv2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FqBh2PNiQ-npPhfpbHkCiIupRudTv2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fl_Z0wCX1NXOrVH0NNFLNHYpC1RBv2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fl_Z0wCX1NXOrVH0NNFLNHYpC1RBv2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fl_Z0wCX1NXOrVH0NNFLNHYpC1RBv2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FsYfHxSO26d81IJASQ2PCJnPOZ27v2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FsYfHxSO26d81IJASQ2PCJnPOZ27v2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FsYfHxSO26d81IJASQ2PCJnPOZ27v2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fsh9NTHnSRQfg9Lh-ntsu_k3WKw7v2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fsh9NTHnSRQfg9Lh-ntsu_k3WKw7v2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fsh9NTHnSRQfg9Lh-ntsu_k3WKw7v2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FmzoATl_ikmSh7lw3K6dYpdmGuDov2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FmzoATl_ikmSh7lw3K6dYpdmGuDov2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FmzoATl_ikmSh7lw3K6dYpdmGuDov2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fnrl0MAVOSx98EW17FYpV53Ystcjv2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fnrl0MAVOSx98EW17FYpV53Ystcjv2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fnrl0MAVOSx98EW17FYpV53Ystcjv2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fj3jD2G26DjfX-Dhfq-i6DJq9Sl1v2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fj3jD2G26DjfX-Dhfq-i6DJq9Sl1v2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fj3jD2G26DjfX-Dhfq-i6DJq9Sl1v2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FtA3xzv0k7XfTj_fF909sDjSjs3av2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FtA3xzv0k7XfTj_fF909sDjSjs3av2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FtA3xzv0k7XfTj_fF909sDjSjs3av2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FjieClzZQLpJwltyYzvwKwNmKzuVv2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FjieClzZQLpJwltyYzvwKwNmKzuVv2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FjieClzZQLpJwltyYzvwKwNmKzuVv2.png"></picture>]]></description>
